==Useful Info==
'''Orc knights''' are a stronger, nastier version of the [[orc warrior]]. They too wield two-handed weapons and wear heavy armour to protect themselves. You'll often find some in the [[Orcish Mines]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
Everything you've learned about orc warriors applies to orc knights, too. This includes their mediocre [[willpower]], making them fairly easy to paralyse or confuse. Unlike orc warriors, however, they can roar a battle-cry, strengthening all lesser orcs around them.

